    "original": "Fun for all ages!\nMy wife has been looking for a karaoke machine for a while and we wanted one with portability to take to parties. This machine delivers!!! Built in screen is great. Microphones are super high quality, feel great in your hands. Setup was a breeze. And the hdmi connectivity was awesome, plugged into our 75” tv seamlessly. Easy to use, our 7 and 9 year olds were singing duets within 15 minutes of setup.10/10 have already recommended to everyone I know.",
    "translation": "所有年龄都能玩得开心\n我妻子找卡拉OK机已经有一段时间，我们想要一台便携、能带去派对的机器。这台完全做到了。内置屏幕很棒，麦克风质量很高、握感很好。设置非常轻松，通过HDMI无缝连接到我们的75英寸电视。操作很容易，我们7岁和9岁的孩子在设置完成15分钟内就开始二重唱。满分推荐，我已经推荐给认识的所有人。",
