    "result": "减少专业现场所需设备和接线，同时让来宾甚至专业歌手都能直接参与。",
    "original": "THIS KARAOKE SPEAKER, THE IKARAOK BREAK X1 IS CRAZY AWESOME!\nThis iKaraok speaker right out of the box was pretty ready to roll. It was packed super well, and had a great instruction manual. All I had to do is just log into my singing programs and YouTube and we were off! The sound quality really kicks, amazing Bass , clear vocals, a great selection of Vocal Effects (You can even change the effects and vocal volume on the microphone).The speaker and packaging design was so well thought out! Carrying Strap, a spot to plug in a USB Thumbdrive, MicroSD Card, a port to plug more mics in and a guitar! so you can play around. But one of the best thinks is the Android Tablet that controls it. Its smooth, and can turn 360 degrees! You can all your favorite singing apps on the iKaraoke Break X1!After trying it at a home karaoke party we brought it to a local pub that doesn't have karaoke and they let us hook it to their TV and it was so easy. We did it by HDMI out but also could have via VideoCast if it was a smart TV.  The Sound filled the whole pub easily, even some professional singers joined in and were blown away!You can also change the light design on the speakers, and connect to other iKarao Speakers! We put it on a small speaker stand as there is speaker stand port on the bottom. The battery lasted about 8.5 hours when we used it just on battery power at our House Party and the mics conveniently charge within the unit and they tuck away in the speaker!The iKarao Break X1 has so many ways to use it! This is perfect for a singer, performer, and karaoke enthusiast! I feel like I have only scratched the surface on figuring out what this speaker can fully do!!I liked it so much we just purchased the new small portable iKarao Shell S1 version! I can't wait to get my hands on it!!",
    "translation": "这台iKarao Break X1卡拉OK音箱太棒了\n开箱后几乎立刻就能使用，包装很好，也有清楚的说明。我只需登录唱歌应用和YouTube就能开始。声音有力，低音和人声清晰，麦克风可调效果与音量。设计考虑周到：有肩带、USB、存储卡、额外麦克风和吉他接口，Android触屏还能360度旋转。我们先在家庭卡拉OK派对试用，之后又带到一家原本没有卡拉OK的酒吧，通过HDMI接电视，很容易就让声音覆盖整个酒吧，甚至有专业歌手加入。家庭派对仅靠电池使用约8.5小时，麦克风会在机内充电和收纳。它适合歌手、表演者和卡拉OK爱好者，用法很多。我们非常喜欢，后来又购买了更小的Shell S1。",
