    "original": "Wonderful experience\nThe unit is very self contained with a long life battery.  The cordless microphones have a charging spot located within the unit as well, actually a wonderful design.  The screen, about the size of an iPad, rotates front and back, so you can solo practice, and then perform to a group.  It connects to a few different apps and of course YouTube and the internet. Definitely an upgrade from our previous Karaoke machine.",
