    "original": "Works OK, limited information\nI bought this for my office party. At home, it worked with the WIFI, it did not work at the party location (hotel ballroom WIFI), I used bluetooth and my phone.  The Karofun subscription did not have a 6 month free option (as indicated in the product description) so I paid.  A song listed as available would not play, not sure why that was.  YouTube App is shown on the machine but not preloaded, so I get a message that this is not available to me.  I do not find information about how to add this app, if that is possible.  I would be happier about this purchase if the instructions available, even if online, were less bare bones.",
