    "original": "Great But Tablet Needs Improvement\nSo I’ve had this for a little over 8 months now and so far it’s been a great quick-take-anywhere karaoke speaker kit.  It works well and is easy to set up.  The sound is super and loud for its size.  But, there is a flaw that is quite frustrating when you’re in the mood.  It’s the tablet.  It kinda freezes or skips when using.  At times it seems like it’s doing its own thing.  I’m thinking it’s probably because the tablet has a slow processor.  That’s what it seems like.  And it’s not my internet speed.I had seen other reviews with the same issue but went ahead and got it anyway.  It still works great with Bluetooth on your phone or even the tablet, but it does gets annoying when it starts lagging.  Also, the volume selector is not set right in the program because when you adjust the knob, you can see on the screen that it jumps from 33%,43%,57%,69% etc..  the volume doesn’t move up or down by one’s.  And for the price,  well after using it for a while, it does seem a little on the high end.  Would I have paid that much for what I see on it now?  Mmm… probably not.",
    "translation": "很好，但平板需要改进\n使用八个多月后，这仍是一套容易携带、容易设置、声音响亮的卡拉OK音箱。但平板令人沮丧：使用时会冻结、跳动，有时像在自行操作，看起来像处理器过慢，而且不是网络速度问题。我买前见过相同评论但仍决定购买。用手机蓝牙仍能工作，不过平板延迟很烦；音量程序也没有正确设置，旋钮会从33%跳到43%、57%、69%，不能逐级调节。以这个价格和长期体验来看，我现在大概不会再付这么多。",
